data.description: FANTASTIC CRAFTSMAN HOME IN PARKSIDE VILLAGE!  Large open kitchen w/stainless appliances, granite countertop w/tiled backsplash, granite top island w/breakfast bar, walk-in pantry & hardwood flooring. Family Room w/hardwood flooring & tile surround fireplace.  Dining Room w/coffered ceiling, judges paneling and hardwood flooring. Office on main level. Vaulted Master Bedroom and tiled Master Bath with his & hers granite top vanities and his & hers walk-in closets.  Three Guest Bedrooms upstairs - 2 have closets and one has a walk-in closet.  Tiled Guest Bathroom in hallway w/granite top double vanity & shower/tub. Tiled Laundry Room upstairs.  Drop zone w/built-ins on main.  Covered vaulted Game Day Porch w/stone surround fireplace.
